# ✅ Security Checklist (DO NOT SKIP)

✅ Refresh token in **HTTP‑only cookie**  
✅ Access token **NOT** in localStorage  
✅ Short access token expiry  
✅ Rotate refresh tokens (advanced)  
✅ HTTPS only

***

# 🔴 Common Mistakes

❌ Store refresh token in localStorage  
❌ Access token with long expiry  
❌ No refresh endpoint  
❌ JS‑accessible cookies

